S.FORM: Cedric Ball nalecuhan i Worcester, Massachusetts, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. 4 bulad 16 demiad, 1968 a mihca, Cedric Ball, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
